article.headline: Croskey scores 20 as South Carolina State defeats Alabama A&M 82-70
article.description: — Omar Croskey scored 20 points as South Carolina State beat Alabama A&M 82-70 on Friday night.
article.linkText: Croskey scores 20 as South Carolina State defeats Alabama A&M 82-70
article.story: HUNTSVILLE, Ala. -- — Omar Croskey scored 20 points as South Carolina State beat Alabama A&M 82-70 on Friday night. Croskey went 7 of 12 from the field (6 for 9 from 3-point range) for the Bulldogs (3-3). Davion Everett scored 12 points while finishing 5 of 6 from the floor and added five rebounds. The Bulldogs (3-3) were led in scoring by Anthony Bryant and Chad Moodie with 16 points apiece. Lorenzo Downey had 14 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
